### Module 04 — hit the slow server manually before you load-test

@base = http://localhost:3004

### Baseline — no cache, blocks on DB latency
GET {{base}}/hot

### CPU-bound, blocks the event loop
GET {{base}}/cpu

### 50 sequential Redis calls per request
GET {{base}}/n-plus-1

### Sends 200 products in one response
GET {{base}}/all

### The cache key changes every request — cache is useless
GET {{base}}/broken-cache/1

### A working cached endpoint for comparison
GET {{base}}/good/1
GET {{base}}/good/1
